OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cstripped of MBE
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby star Stuart Hogg
OL,7,Fhas been stripped of his MBE.
OL,9,FIn 2024 the 33-year-old from Hawick
OL,10,Fpleaded guilty to a domestic abuse
OL,11,Fcharge against his estranged wife and
OL,12,Fwas handed a one-year community
OL,13,Fpayback order at Selkirk Sheriff Court
OL,14,Fand fined #600, with an additional #40
OL,15,Fvictim surcharge.
OL,17,FHogg won 100 Scotland caps during an
OL,18,F11-year international career and
OL,19,Ftoured three times with the British
OL,20,Fand Irish Lions.
