OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cstripped of MBE
OL,6,FHe was awarded the MBE for services to
OL,7,Frugby. A notice posted today in the
OL,8,FThe Gazette - the official public
OL,9,Frecord - said the honour "shall be
OL,10,Fcancelled and annulled and that his
OL,11,Fname shall be erased from the Register
OL,12,Fof the said Order."
OL,14,FLast year the SNP's Westminster leader
OL,15,Fhad called for Hogg to be stripped of
OL,16,Fthe honour. Stephen Flynn made the
OL,17,Fcall in the Commons, with First
OL,18,FMinister John Swinney agreeing that it
OL,19,Fwas "reasonable and understandable".
